main event: A 52-year-old female resident of Old Bridge, New Jersey, observed a dark, oval-shaped object moving slowly in the sky on April 6, 1967.
interesting points: The observer described the object as dark in color and approximately 30 feet in diameter,The object was at a high altitude without any accompanying aircraft,The sighting lasted for several minutes before the object disappeared from view,Another witness reported a similar black oval-shaped object hovering 500 feet above ground,The case was classified as unidentified after thorough investigation.
sighted object: dark oval-shaped object in the sky
witness description: A 52-year-old female resident and another witness named Durk Harrison.
